Text.Value: No... Ulma... leader of my tribe...
Dread... creature... but not the one... I hunt...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*
Much. Nothing... you can spend...
Who is this wise woman?
Vampire... Astarion...
Leave.
Do you have anything of value?
Capture... return... Baldur's Gate...
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*
What were you going to do to me?
Who are you?
Why did you need me alive? Why not destroy me?
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Who sent you? Was it Cazador?
Gandrel... hunter...
What's your business with this Astarion?
Our children... he knows... where they are...
What are you hunting?
Our children... you know... where they are...
Wise... woman... questions...
What brought you to this place?
What's your business with Astarion?

Synopsis: We can speak to Gandrel if he dies - he'll hint at his mission to hunt Astarion on behalf of Maiden Fel. Separate options if it's Astarion himself speaking to him.
